   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Ptolemaios, son of Ptolemaios, a former member of the agoranomos collegium, to Onesios, son of Amerimnos, a cook, greetings. I have received from you the 300 silver drachmas which you received on account of an advanced payment and I make no charge against you. 3rd year of Lucius Septimius Severus Pertinax Augustus. Pharmouthi 8."</ab>
